      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f0"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "CUBE (side a):\n  Volume = a^3\n  TSA = 6a^2,  LSA = 4a^2\n  Diagonal = a*sqrt(3)\n\nCUBOID (l x b x h):\n  Volume = l*b*h\n  TSA = 2(lb + bh + hl)\n  LSA = 2h(l + b)\n  Diagonal = sqrt(l^2 + b^2 + h^2)",
