    {
      "id": "el_11",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 125,
      "width": 211,
      "height": 172,
      "text": "SPHERE (r):\n  Volume = (4/3)*pi*r^3\n  SA = 4*pi*r^2\n\nHEMISPHERE (r):\n  Volume = (2/3)*pi*r^3\n  CSA = 2*pi*r^2\n  TSA = 3*pi*r^2\n\nHOLLOW CYLINDER (R, r, h):\n  Volume = pi*h*(R^2 - r^2)",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
