    {
      "id": "el_25",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 688,
      "width": 267,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: V = 12×8×5 = 480\nStep 2: TSA = 2(96+40+60) = 392\n  Diag = √(144+64+25) = √233\n\nTRICK:\nTSA = 2(lb+bh+hl)\nJust compute 3 face areas, double sum\n\n  ┌──────────┐\n  │ 12×8×5   │\n  └──────────┘\n\nAnswer: V=480, TSA=392 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
