      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: V = π×49×10 = 1540\nStep 2: CSA = 2π×7×10 = 440\n  TSA = 2π×7×17 = 748\n\nTRICK:\nCSA = 2πrh (just the curved part)\nTSA = CSA + 2 circles = 2πr(r+h)\nπ = 22/7 when r=7 → clean numbers!\n\nAnswer: V=1540, CSA=440, TSA=748 ✓",
