    {
      "id": "el_35",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1056,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: l = √(36+64) = √100 = 10\nStep 2: V = (1/3)π×36×8 = 301.71\n  CSA = π×6×10 = 188.57\n\nTRICK:\nPythagorean triplet: 6,8,10\nCone V = (1/3) × cylinder V\n\n    /\\  l=10\n   /  \\ h=8\n  /____\\ r=6\n\nAnswer: l=10, V=301.71, CSA=188.57 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 3500,
