      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_4"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: l = √(36+64) = √100 = 10\nStep 2: V = (1/3)π×36×8 = 301.71\n  CSA = π×6×10 = 188.57\n\nTRICK:\nPythagorean triplet: 6,8,10\nCone V = (1/3) × cylinder V\n\n    /\\  l=10\n   /  \\ h=8\n  /____\\ r=6\n\nAnswer: l=10, V=301.71, CSA=188.57 ✓",
