      "x": 535,
      "y": 1040,
      "width": 195,
      "height": 159,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: V = (4/3)π×343\n  = 4/3×22×49 = 1437.33\nStep 2: SA = 4π×49 = 616\n\nTRICK:\nSA = 4πr² (4 circles!)\nV = (4/3)πr³\nWith r=7: SA=616, V=1437.33\n\nAnswer: V=1437.33, SA=616 ✓",
