      "y": 1056,
      "width": 267,
      "height": 159,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: V = (2/3)π×2744 = 5749.33\nStep 2: CSA = 2π×196 = 1232\n  TSA = 3π×196 = 1848\n\nTRICK:\nHemisphere TSA = 3πr² (curved + base)\nCSA = 2πr² (just dome)\nTSA = CSA + πr² (add flat circle)\n\nAnswer: V=5749.33, TSA=1848 ✓",
