    {
      "id": "el_50",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1424,
      "width": 202,
      "height": 159,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: V = πh(R²-r²)\n  = 22/7×20×(100-64)\nStep 2: = 22/7×720 = 2262.86\n\nTRICK:\nV = πh(R²-r²) = πh(R+r)(R-r)\n= 22/7×20×18×2 = 2262.86\nFactor form often easier!\n\nAnswer: 2262.86 cm³ ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
