      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1408,
      "width": 209,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: V = (πh/3)(R²+r²+Rr)\n  = (22/7×6/3)(64+16+32)\nStep 2: = (44/7)(112) = 704\n\nTRICK:\nFrustum V = (πh/3)(R²+r²+Rr)\nThink: average of 3 areas × h\n\n    ┌──┐ r=4\n   /    \\ h=6\n  └──────┘ R=8\n\nAnswer: 704 cm³ ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
