      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1424,
      "width": 245,
      "height": 159,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Volume = 50×40×3 = 6000 m³\nStep 2: Time = 6000/25 = 240 min\n  = 4 hours\n\nTRICK:\nTime = Volume needed / flow rate\n= (L×B×rise) / rate\n= 6000/25 = 240 min = 4 hrs\n\nAnswer: 4 hours ✓",
