    {
      "id": "el_70",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1776,
      "width": 231,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Sphere touches all faces\n  Diameter = side = 10, r = 5\nStep 2: V = (4/3)π×125 = 523.81\n\nTRICK:\nSphere in cube: r = side/2\nCube in sphere: side = 2r/√3\n\n  ┌────────┐\n  │ (   )  │ r = side/2\n  └────────┘\n\nAnswer: 523.81 cm³ ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
