    {
      "id": "el_75",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1776,
      "width": 245,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Cyl V = π×9×10 = 90π\nStep 2: Cone V = (1/3)π×9×4 = 12π\n  Total = 102π = 320.57\n\nTRICK:\nCone = (1/3) of same-size cylinder\nCyl:Cone = 3:1 ratio always\n\n    /\\  cone h=4\n   /  \\\n  |    | cyl h=10\n  |____|  r=3\n\nAnswer: 320.57 cm³ ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
