    {
      "id": "el_80",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 2158,
      "width": 231,
      "height": 173,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: V = πr²h\n  New V = π(1.2r)²(0.9h)\nStep 2: = 1.44×0.9×πr²h = 1.296V\n  Change = 29.6% increase\n\nTRICK:\nr has power 2, h has power 1\nFactor = (1.2)²×(0.9) = 1.296\nScaling: dimensions^power\n\nAnswer: 29.6% increase ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
